title: Ultra (Luna Brothers/Image) Complete
description:
Ultra is an eight-issue limited series created by the Luna Brothers and published by Image Comics.  The series&#039; centrers on Pearl Penalosa, who is also a superheroine called Ultra. The story deals not only with traditional superhero comics themes, like fighting supervillains, but concentrates mainly on how being a superhero affects Pearl&#039;s personal life. One reviewer described the series as "Sex and the City with female heroes".
